title: Real Bitches of Beverly Hills with Lucas Cruikshank and Matt Fawcus
description: Jackie sips rosé with Lucas Cruikshank and Matt Fawcus as they passionately recap this season of Real Housewives of Beverly Hills. Life isn't all diamonds and rosé, but this podcast sure is.
